  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-03295', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-097-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '在不需媒介物質的情況下，兩物體雖不接觸，熱仍可直接由高溫物體傳至低溫物體之現象稱為：', '["熱擴散", "熱傳導", "熱對流", "熱輻射"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "75a2171b794e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097090", "c": "302", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技消防設備人員、不動產經紀人、專責報關人員、保險從業人員、中醫師、驗船師考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-03296', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-097-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者為火載量（FireLoad）之定義？', '["單位體積之可燃物量（kg/m3）", "單位面積之可燃物量（kg/m2）", "單位時間之可燃物量（kg/min）", "單位時間之發熱量（kcal/min）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "75a2171b794e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097090", "c": "302", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技消防設備人員、不動產經紀人、專責報關人員、保險從業人員、中醫師、驗船師考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-03297', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-097-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於煙囪效應的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["當室內溫度升高，煙囪效應的中性帶向下偏移", "上部開口越大，中性帶會上移", "火災發生在中性帶以下區域，煙會隨著煙囪效應迅速由垂直通道向上竄升", "火災發生於中性帶以上的樓層，則煙將由建築物該層的開口直接排出起火樓層外"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "75a2171b794e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097090", "c": "302", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技消防設備人員、不動產經紀人、專責報關人員、保險從業人員、中醫師、驗船師考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-03298', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-097-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '燃燒中的天花板會向地面放射大量輻射熱，促進地面可燃物的燃燒速度，此種現象即為密閉空間具有的何種效果？', '["熱對流回饋效果", "輻射能回饋效果", "熱傳導回饋效果", "煙囪效應"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "75a2171b794e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097090", "c": "302", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技消防設備人員、不動產經紀人、專責報關人員、保險從業人員、中醫師、驗船師考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-03299', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-097-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設燃料燃燒所需的理論空氣量為Lo，實際需要空氣量為La，則La=K×Lo，其中K>1，此K值稱為：', '["空氣過剩率", "空氣容積", "空氣比", "廢氣量"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:27+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "75a2171b794e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "097090", "c": "302", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "097", "exam_name": "097年第一次專技消防設備人員、不動產經紀人、專責報關人員、保險從業人員、中醫師、驗船師考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL)
